summary: Rare 3 bedroom corner unit in the resort like Stadium Lofts.  Only 8 units in the entire complex are close to this size but none as beautiful.  Once you enter this amazing unit you are transported to your own elegant resort with a tropical island feel.  From the polished sand colored Italian porcelain tiles to the soaring ceilings, and well appointed finishes this unit affords a relaxing lifestyle. Enjoy the Disneyland fireworks views from the spacious oversized balcony. Dual pane windows on 2 sides bring in tons of natural light.  Spacious kitchen with black granite counters, upgraded black appliances, breakfast bar computer desk/counter,and lots of windows to allow for views from anywhere in the kitchen.  Additional upgrades included crown molding throughout reverse osmosis,custom window casings, and walk in closets. Enjoy amenities such as heated pool and spa, dry sauna, a full gym,Clubhouse with full kitchen, game room with pool table, large screen TV, BBQ areas, & meeting rooms.  This unit comes with 2 deeded parking spots and a rare large storage unit.  Located in the heart of Orange County, this Urban complex is close to Angel Stadium, Disneyland, UCI medical Center, The Orange Block, Honda Center, Anaheim Metrolink station and easy freeway access.

summary: Situated on a corner lot, this spacious home offers 3 bedrooms plus a large loft that can be converted to a 4th bedroom.  With more than 2600 square feet of living space; this home has an elegant presentation with upgraded Travertine like flooring, recessed lighting, cathedral ceilings and an abundance of windows. The upgraded gourmet kitchen has new dark wood cabinetry and back splash, quartz counters, high end stainless appliances and a large center island with conversation seating for five. Enjoy the serenity of the huge Master Suite with private retreat and dual sided fireplace.  This space offers an enormous walk in closet and private bath with his and hers dual sinks, separate spacious sunken tub & enclosed glass shower. Large family room with fireplace is open to the kitchen and perfect for entertaining.  Inside laundry, new vinyl fencing, 2 car attached garage with built in cabinets, walking distance to award winning gold ribbon Running Springs elementary school.
